---
import "../../styles/hero/HeroContent.css";
---

<div class="hero-text-content">
    <div class="badge-new">
        <span class="dot"></span> Contrata sin fronteras
    </div>
    <h1>Contratar talento remoto en LATAM para empresas en España</h1>
    <p class="hero-description">
        En Oberstaff hacemos posible <span class="highlight"
            >contratar talento</span
        > cualificado en Latinoamérica mediante reclutamiento remoto, integración
        rápida y ahorro operativo sin riesgos legales.
    </p>
    <p class="social-proof">Más de 5.000 empresas confían en Oberstaff.</p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/home" class="btn-primary"
            >Agenda una llamada gratis <iconify-icon
                icon="solar:alt-arrow-right-linear"
                class="btn-icon-right"></iconify-icon></a
        >
        <a href="/home" class="btn-secondary">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:play-circle-bold" class="btn-icon-left"
            ></iconify-icon> Ver cómo funciona
        </a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-footer-note">
        <iconify-icon
            icon="solar:check-circle-bold"
            class="note-icon"
            color="#ff66cc"></iconify-icon> Sin tarjeta de crédito · Sin compromiso
    </p>
</div>

<style>
    .hero-text-content {
        max-width: 550px;
    }

    .badge-new {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        background: #f0f0ff;
        color: #5c5cff;
        padding: 4px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .badge-new .dot {
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        background: #5c5cff;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin-right: 8px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 46px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.1;
        color: #1b1b1b;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        letter-spacing: -1.2px;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .hero-description {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #666;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        max-width: 450px;
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }

    .highlight {
        color: #ff66cc;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .social-proof {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #464951;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #ff66cc;
        color: #1b1b1b;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 102, 204, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
        background-color: white;
        color: #1b1b1b;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: 2px solid #1b1b1b;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 13px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
        background-color: #1b1b1b;
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover iconify-icon {
        color: #ff66cc;
    }

    .btn-icon-right {
        margin-left: 8px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .btn-icon-left {
        margin-right: 8px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .note-icon {
        color: #ff66cc;
        vertical-align: middle;
        margin-right: 4px;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-footer-note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #999;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
        }
        .hero-description {
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .hero-actions {
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
    }
</style>
